{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "cyna-api-complete",
    "name": "CYNA API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for CYNA e-commerce B2B platform.\n\n## Authentication\nUser and Admin endpoints use Bearer JWT tokens. Tokens are automatically managed via collection-level scripts.\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Import this collection and the CYNA-Local environment\n2. Run **Auth - User > Login** to get an access token\n3. All authenticated endpoints will automatically use the token\n\n## Admin Flow\n1. Run **Auth - Admin > Admin Login** (sends 2FA code)\n2. Run **Auth - Admin > Verify 2FA** with the code from email\n3. Admin endpoints are now accessible",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{accessToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Auto-refresh token if expired (with 30s margin)",
          "const tokenExpiresAt = pm.environment.get('tokenExpiresAt');",
          "const accessToken = pm.environment.get('accessToken');",
          "",
          "if (accessToken && tokenExpiresAt && Date.now() > (parseInt(tokenExpiresAt) - 30000)) {",
          "    pm.sendRequest({",
          "        url: pm.environment.get('baseUrl') + '/' + pm.environment.get('apiPrefix') + '/auth/refresh-token',",
          "        method: 'POST',",
          "        header: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },",
          "        body: { mode: 'raw', raw: JSON.stringify({}) }",
          "    }, function (err, res) {",
          "        if (!err && res.code === 200) {",
          "            const json = res.json();",
          "            pm.environment.set('accessToken', json.accessToken);",
          "            pm.environment.set('tokenExpiresAt', String(Date.now() + (json.expiresIn * 1000)));",
          "        }",
          "    });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "apiPrefix",
      "value": "api/v1"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
